metaDescription: Add chat, conference, real time collaboration and communication (PBX, VoIP, P2P) capabilities, bots and more to your business applications.
mainHtml:
Documentation

Telephony service

LTS release 4.0.0Publiée le 2022-12-21

Telephony

This services manages PBX phone calls in a conversation. so it manages PBX calls between your PABX associated phone and a recipient's phone. If you don't have this service activated for your Rainbow user, all these methods will return an error when called. The main methods and events proposed in that service allow to:
- Know if this service is activated or not for the connected user,
- Know the version of the agent (deployed on the PBX) that monitors your line,
- Handle the basic telephony services: Make a call, take a call, hold a call, retrieve a call and release a call,
- Listen to the call state change Depending the agent version deployed, some services can return an error (unavailable service) when called

Emits: event:RAINBOW_ONTELEPHONYSTARTED, event:RAINBOW_ONTELEPHONYSTOPPED, event:RAINBOW_ONTELEPHONYCALLSTATECHANGED, event:RAINBOW_ONVOIPCALLSTATECHANGED, event:RAINBOW_ONTELEPHONYFORWARDSTATECHANGED, event:RAINBOW_ONCALLNOMADICEVENT, event:RAINBOW_ONVOIPSTARTED, event:RAINBOW_ONVOIPSTOPPED, event:RAINBOW_ONVOICEMESSAGEUPDATED, event:RAINBOW_TELEPHONYMUTE, event:RAINBOW_ONTELEPHONYMODEUPDATED, event:RAINBOW_ONFORWARDMODEUPDATED

telephony.transferCall(activeCall, heldCall) ⇒ Promise

Transfer a held call to the active call Both active and held calls should be of type "Phone". This feature works only with the telephony calls. Do not use with VoIP calls. User should have transfer rights NB (for only OXO/OXE): This API can be also be used to transfer the held call while the other "active" call is still in outgoing ringing state; This is called transfer on ringing;

Kind: instance method of Telephony
Returns: Promise - Return the SDK OK object in case of success or an SDK error object
Access: public

ParamTypeDescription
activeCallobjectThe active call
heldCallobjectThe held call to transfer to the activeCall

telephony.subscribeToCCDEvents(handler) ⇒ Subscription

Subscribe to updates on the CCD Agent (all events are of RBEvent type {name: string, data:any}); The name of the event is ON_CCD_UPDATE_EVENT which will provide an update of the current CCD informations: { passwordNeeded: boolean agentId: string passwordPresence: boolean currentGroupId: string logActivated: boolean wrapUpActivated: boolean withdrawalActivated: boolean pauseActivated: boolean state: string reason: string }

Kind: instance method of Telephony
Returns: Subscription - Returns RxJS Subscription
Access: public

ParamTypeDescription
handleranyThe call-back function that will be subscribed to the RxJS subject
